{"tid":1000811,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"神劇重溫-Unnatural","createTime":"2019-01-29T16:19:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T15:11:27.000Z","uid":225331,"like":103,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"623de487f3dcedd1a7129833c05ffada81410145","tid":1000811,"uid":225331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:19:24.000Z","msg":"近排因為無野做重睇左次Unnatural <br />\n呢套劇真係百看不厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先有個完美女演員 石原里美做女主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xzTKyQ2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxzTKyQ2.png&h=13375ba8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vwrj7a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvwrj7a4.png&h=47b3be1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後仲有一首好好聽嘅主題曲 Lemon <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZLvm7JTJp40\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZLvm7JTJp40&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMHs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=740de74b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZLvm7JTJp40</a><br />\n而且每次放首歌出嚟嘅時間都啱啱好 成功帶動觀眾情緒 唔似某個電影台係又放唔係又放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後講下劇情 每一集都好成功由驗屍再慢慢帶出一個背後感人嘅故事、訊息或者諷刺現今社會<br />\n<br />\n利申：重睇有感而發  不喜就屌細力啲"},{"pid":"53876e3ba1e0d090cbe8505269ea724c4b01121a","tid":1000811,"uid":225331,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:24:03.000Z","msg":"尤其係第八集個死者老豆知道自己個仔唔係惹禍而係救人而死同掛住屋企嗰下特別感人 同埋六郎個老豆話佢如果要留喺UDI就唔洗返屋企嗰下<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f14062391b405cdb4e9d5a8567859ae4e17e1050","tid":1000811,"uid":225331,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:34:31.000Z","msg":"一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"987b48fded24d99ed5505a744ddaadb66ca9c9fa","tid":1000811,"uid":225331,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:35:26.000Z","msg":"希望有更多人睇到呢套神劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd9be2d5c19c1d9e83fb74fe8848babc08d7cdf","tid":1000811,"uid":29214,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:35:56.000Z","msg":"期待第二季"},{"pid":"0b7a5b0a8900b9307a3b5824b428958c448cf436","tid":1000811,"uid":20631,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:36:50.000Z","msg":"無耐之前姐 唔洗講到重溫咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47d1ba351c4758d1a010b863cd72997fad8d9b3c","tid":1000811,"uid":225331,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b7a5b0a8900b9307a3b5824b428958c448cf436","tid":1000811,"uid":20631,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:36:50.000Z","msg":"無耐之前姐 唔洗講到重溫咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:38:05.000Z","msg":"用錯字 Sor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49c2521a9ac1aaf56eda8c218fad1d937f7fb254","tid":1000811,"uid":225331,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0cd9be2d5c19c1d9e83fb74fe8848babc08d7cdf","tid":1000811,"uid":29214,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:35:56.000Z","msg":"期待第二季"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:38:22.000Z","msg":"希望有啦<img src=\"/asse